3.5 -> LR- ~0.4 -> PMID:8675081","guid":"Jr7pBX2_R82ixOT1JZOjGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"284","parent":"267","text":"HALLAZGOS ENDOSCOPICOS (Forrest)","guid":"UaSu9VgJQ2izY5549pgKhw","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"Forrest Ia (sangrado arterial activo) -> resangrado 55% sin tratamiento","guid":"p6j2aztFQoOH1fz3xoeSIQ","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"284","text":"Forrest Ib (sangrado venoso activo) -> resangrado 22%","guid":"GJMezBjISxixTOpLWvVGrA","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"284","text":"Forrest IIa (vaso visible) -> resangrado 43%","guid":"caTKfu4NSC2OqOUysMIVnw","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"284","text":"Forrest IIb (coagulo adherido) -> resangrado 22%","guid":"UbckCCaJQHi0Pl47NvEhUQ","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"284","text":"Forrest IIc (mancha plana) -> resangrado 7%","guid":"yPdFzC7CRqaKS600WO7CVg","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"284","text":"Forrest III (base limpia) -> resangrado 5%","guid":"-ikMIRKfQxigPjuaWB2x_g","children":[]}]},{"id":"291","parent":"267","text":"INTERPRETACION","guid":"RioZVW8BQaGd9KYNOD825w","children":[{"id":"292","parent":"291","text":"LR+ >10 o LR- <0.1 -> cambio GRANDE","guid":"uZsOjWOHQJuu_1rTDbftGQ","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"291","text":"LR+ 5-10 o LR- 0.1-0.2 -> cambio MODERADO","guid":"d-eFrLBWTmW_WOLBrhVQGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"294","parent":"267","text":"GERIATRIA","guid":"4FR2SrOXQSSjvuFSyWdfPw","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"AM + AINEs/AAS + delirium + anemia -> sospechar HDA aun sin melena reportada","guid":"oShb1_nOTdmhtxwZ44iekQ","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"294","text":"Tacto rectal OBLIGATORIO","guid":"MCYK-xpeSwCvbeoH9IYW_w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"297","parent":"0","text":"REFERENCIAS","guid":"ZbY9yR4-QHiyVBq_LYQZXg","children":[{"id":"298","parent":"297","text":"ACG 2021 Upper GI Bleeding Guidelines (Laine et al)","guid":"EXvRZT8xQKmKJgtI2ohApw","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"297","text":"BSG 2019 Acute Lower GI Bleeding Guidelines","guid":"VDKhhZ-NSx-Z1RE5ieD2-w","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"297","text":"TRIGGER trial → transfusión restrictiva en HDA (Villanueva et al, NEJM 2013)","guid":"LETmllTTSzWYCJHzXcafWA","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"297","text":"HALT-IT trial → ácido tranexámico en HDA (Lancet 2020)","guid":"gPzcFq4ITkufv1L_sIzS0Q","children":[]},{"id":"302","parent":"297","text":"Baveno VII → consenso hipertensión portal (de Franchis et al, J Hepatol 2022)","guid":"m8P8VHVXRPOB8t4WRyEWRg","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"297","text":"International Consensus Upper GI Bleeding (Barkun et al, Ann Intern Med 2019)","guid":"gKDfB7u7SLW5S1LTN08Lqg","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"297","text":"Minsal Chile → GPC Hemorragia Digestiva Alta 2013","guid":"VVsSEBy2S468MCNNngUyPw","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":304,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Medicina de Urgencia","folder":"MUE - Medicina de Urgencia","filename":"MUE_Hemorragia_Digestiva","id":"map_2507","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"MUE_Hemorragia_Digestiva"}